me as in the $q \\rightarrow 0$ limit of the $q$-state Potts\nmodel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Feb 2015 17:43:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2015 20:44:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2015 17:51:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
