am\nfollow-up observations could constrain the properties of matter ejected by the\nbinary and the equation of state of dense nuclear matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Feb 2015 04:10:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2015 20:18:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2015 15:41:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-13"}
